{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":1058,"text":"Today I'm going to show you an electric vehicle"},{"time":4636,"text":"that weighs less than a bicycle,"},{"time":8542,"text":"that you can carry with you anywhere,"},{"time":11888,"text":"that you can charge off a normal wall outlet in 15 minutes,"},{"time":16380,"text":"and you can run it for 1,000 kilometers"},{"time":18628,"text":"on about a dollar of electricity."},{"time":20980,"text":"But when I say the word electric vehicle,"},{"time":23268,"text":"people think about vehicles. They think about cars"},{"time":26156,"text":"and motorcycles and bicycles, and the vehicles that you use every day."},{"time":29874,"text":"But if you come about it from a different perspective,"},{"time":32170,"text":"you can create some more interesting,"},{"time":34472,"text":"more novel concepts."}]},{"cues":[{"time":37152,"text":"So we built something."},{"time":39408,"text":"I've got some of the pieces in my pocket here."},{"time":42102,"text":"So this is the motor."},{"time":44192,"text":"This motor has enough power to take you"},{"time":45801,"text":"up the hills of San Francisco at about 20 miles per hour,"},{"time":49608,"text":"about 30 kilometers an hour,"},{"time":51434,"text":"and this battery, this battery right here"},{"time":55524,"text":"has about six miles of range, or 10 kilometers,"},{"time":59472,"text":"which is enough to cover about half of the car trips"},{"time":62275,"text":"in the U.S. alone."},{"time":64672,"text":"But the best part about these components"},{"time":66451,"text":"is that we bought them at a toy store."},{"time":68648,"text":"These are from remote control airplanes."},{"time":71072,"text":"And the performance of these things has gotten so good"},{"time":73216,"text":"that if you think about vehicles a little bit differently,"},{"time":75512,"text":"you can really change things."}]},{"cues":[{"time":77015,"text":"So today we're going to show you one example"},{"time":79012,"text":"of how you can use this."},{"time":81089,"text":"Pay attention to not only how fun this thing is,"},{"time":83888,"text":"but also how the portability that comes with this"},{"time":86966,"text":"can totally change the way you interact with a city like San Francisco."}]},{"cues":[{"time":91313,"text":"(Music)"},{"time":110765,"text":"[6 Mile Range] [Top Speed Near 20mph]"},{"time":113786,"text":"[Uphill Climbing]"},{"time":132094,"text":"[Regenerative Braking]"}]},{"cues":[{"time":158458,"text":"(Applause)"},{"time":164517,"text":"(Cheers)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":168829,"text":"So we're going to show you what this thing can do."},{"time":172122,"text":"It's really maneuverable. You have a hand-held remote,"},{"time":174815,"text":"so you can pretty easily control acceleration, braking,"},{"time":178394,"text":"go in reverse if you like, also have braking."},{"time":189431,"text":"It's incredible just how light this thing is."},{"time":191488,"text":"I mean, this is something you can pick up and carry with you"},{"time":193617,"text":"anywhere you go."}]},{"cues":[{"time":196553,"text":"So I'll leave you with one of the most compelling facts"},{"time":199729,"text":"about this technology and these kinds of vehicles."},{"time":202585,"text":"This uses 20 times less energy"},{"time":205977,"text":"for every mile or kilometer that you travel than a car,"},{"time":209344,"text":"which means not only is this thing fast to charge"},{"time":212977,"text":"and really cheap to build,"},{"time":214666,"text":"but it also reduces the footprint of your energy use"},{"time":218017,"text":"in terms of your transportation."},{"time":219652,"text":"So instead of looking at large amounts of energy needed"},{"time":222411,"text":"for each person in this room to get around in a city,"},{"time":225345,"text":"now you can look at much smaller amounts"},{"time":227465,"text":"and more sustainable transportation."}]},{"cues":[{"time":229905,"text":"So next time you think about a vehicle,"},{"time":231267,"text":"I hope, like us, you're thinking about something new."}]},{"cues":[{"time":234573,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":235711,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}